@chapter Character sets


@cindex @library{vicare containers char-sets}, library
@cindex Library @library{vicare containers char-sets}


The library @library{vicare containers char-sets} handles sets of
characters.

A @dfn{character} is every value for which the application of
@func{char?}  returns @true{}; @dfn{character sets} are values of
disjoint type @code{char-set} representing a number of character in the
available Unicode ranges, @vicareref{stdlib unicode, Unicode}.

